|<math>R = a\left(\frac{T}{2\pi}\right)^2,</math>

<math>a = R\left(\frac{2\pi}{T}\right)^2 \quad (T > 0),</math>

<math>T = 2\pi\sqrt{\frac{R}{a}} \quad (a > 0),</math>

where:

''R'' = 旋轉中心半徑<br>''a'' = 人工重力<br>''T'' = 旋轉一圈所需時間
